<div class="documentation">
  <h1><i class="icon-cogs"></i> [% l('System Configuration') %]</h1>

  <p>[% l('PacketFence allows you to perform advanced system configuration. Among the configuration options, there are:') %]</p>

  <dl>
    <dt>[% l('Main Configuration:') %]</dt> <dd>[% l('This allows you set the DNS name, SMTP information for alerts, default language and more.') %]</dd>
