    <dt>[% l('Cluster:') %]</dt> <dd>[% l('PacketFence supports clustering of 3+ members. You can configure the clustering solution from this module.') %]</dd>
    <dt>[% l('Authentication Methods:') %]</dt> <dd>[% l('EAP methods provided by PacketFence can be changed from this module.') %]</dd>
    <dt>[% l('Node Import') %]</dt> <dd>[% l('The default parameters to be used when importing nodes') %]</dd>
    <dt>[% l('Admin Access:') %]</dt> <dd>[% l('Different access level can be defined for the PacketFence administrative interface from this module.') %]</dd>
  </dl>
</div>
